Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:38.84,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,controlling an army of the dead\Nto attack the royal capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:42.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,was restrained by Fuegoleon, \Nalong with Asta's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:48.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you think of any other way to get \Npeople to acknowledge your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:52.09,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:56.37,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:58.03,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Noâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the Magic Knights were sent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:11.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,far away from the royal \Ncapital with spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:18.01,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I figured they must've had a rather \Nskilled spatial magic user, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:21.89,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,To think they were able \Nto send us all this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.10,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,This is spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:31.90,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Nothing ventured, nothing gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:36.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of the Crimson Lion Kings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:40.36,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon Vermillion, was also\Nsent away somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:43.41,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:47.21,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Yuno was able to escape \Nthe spatial magic attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:50.10,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but while battling a witch who\Nused ash curse magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:55.05,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he ended up losing his sight, \Nhearing, and other senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:56.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.49,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.89,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just tell you one thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.06,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.97,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,hate losing more than anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:15.40,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Spirit Magic: Sylph's Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:37.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:42.05,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:46.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:51.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.20,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.90,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.90,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:05.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:13.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:18.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:24.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.27,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:38.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.53,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Adversity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.83,sign_5488_49_Castle_Town_Kikk,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(984,1)}Castle Town Kikka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.84,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.77,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.85,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.35,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,The way you eat is fantastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.61,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,you shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:21.23,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Eat, eat, and eat some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:22.24,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:26.66,italics,Subordinate 2,0000,0000,0000,,The country's in danger!\NWhat the heck are these two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.31,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not enough, I'll make\Nas much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:31.12,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.10,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.92,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,A witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.80,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,We're being attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.37,main,Subordinate,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we told you we should run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:49.93,main,Subordinate 2,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.83,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, shrimp, we gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.29,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I need... mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.65,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I need to steal some!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.40,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,She's overflowing with mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.37,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,It's glistening on her skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.95,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I need to steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.51,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.52,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.14,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to you? You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:24.55,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.77,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.36,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.93,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:47.20,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This mana... That woman must still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.09,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reaching my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:00.25,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What is this overflowing magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:03.17,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.21,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.97,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.60,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I told you no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.13,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:35.40,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton Creation Magic:\NStrike of the Sleeping Sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.41,main,Subordinate,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.18,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:56.36,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,The food that I cooked with all my soul \Npowered up the shrimp's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:07:01.19,main,Subordinate 2,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! We'll follow you forever, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.81,main,Subordinate,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.08,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,Glad ya liked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:10.45,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,None shall ever lay a finger on my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.95,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,And don't you ever come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.93,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Am I pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.64,main,Hot guy,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.72,main,Hot guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll love you no matter how you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.68,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:48.82,main,Hot guy,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.36,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,My love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.20,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.71,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.96,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:11.09,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My noms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.63,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,A kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:32.61,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That tremendous magical power \NI felt earlier... was from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:38.94,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,A Black Bulls robe... So it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:40.69,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,M-My noms?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:45.42,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Noms? Oh, here. I'm not sure \Nwhat's going on, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.25,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank yâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:49.63,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:09:00.64,italicstop,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My meal-saving prince has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.64,sign_12905_116_Meal_Saving_Prin,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(923,1)}Meal-Saving Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:06.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.40,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.94,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.80,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,N-Name...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.74,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Short ribs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.95,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. They're delicious! Try some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:22.17,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean... Wh-What is {\i1}your{\i0} name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:28.34,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I mean, I like meat, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.00,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,As you'd expect...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:32.21,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That spell wears out my body \Nand uses a ton of mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:34.67,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,But what I was wondering \Nabout is your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:39.16,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I need to learn how to use it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.31,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:50.36,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La... La! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.39,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La la la...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:01.46,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I might as well eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.87,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.27,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather noisy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.77,sign_12905_116_Meal_Saving_Prin,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1034)}King's Quarters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.49,top,King,0000,0000,0000,,Could you shut them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.01,top,King,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for my royal nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.38,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:28.20,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,He should be back any moment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:31.23,sign_12905_116_Meal_Saving_Prin,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1011,1)\fs24}The "He" in Question
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:35.03,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best shrimp ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.07,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:41.26,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,Come see me whenever you're hungry. \NI'll let you eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.89,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.16,sign_15493_144_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,North District
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:52.05,top,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What have you \Ndone with my brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold! He's not the spatial magic user.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That spell pinpointed him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no way the spellcaster \Ncould've cast it from far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Where could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:45.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He was hiding among the corpses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.02,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.91,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd be found if \NI used magic to transform,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:56.57,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,so I went to the trouble of \Nmaking this filthy disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.09,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, an animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.07,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,But it appears that it's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.58,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,What's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.81,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But he's so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's... impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.64,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-His arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.19,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:25.11,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon... Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.12,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible... There's \Nno way Fuegoleon would lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:32.12,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,My brother wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.12,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Fuegoleon's grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:41.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's still intact, which means... he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.91,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.01,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:51.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If only Mimosa were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:00.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... His grimoire is breaking apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:05.95,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold! Your captain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:14.49,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for \Ntalking down to me earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.01,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A magic blast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:45.69,flashback,Fueoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What you lacked to overcome adversity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.49,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,was a righteous heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:55.22,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,A righteous heart?! I've always\Nbeen true to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:15:00.46,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Keep yappin' in the next world,\NFuegoleon Vermillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.29,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,We've completed our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.72,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving before the other \NMagic Knights come back, Rades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:16.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it... right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.12,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:27.40,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eventually kill you and make\Nyou into one of my toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.60,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to that, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:41.87,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This distance... I'm not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.88,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If you move any more while \Nyou're bleeding that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.21,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.98,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of the Crimson \NLion Kings just taught me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.26,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I need to think calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.20,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How can I stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That spatial magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:05.54,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And my sword can...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.56,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.28,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What the hell are\Nyou doing, you little shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.29,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:34.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You have the nerve to say that \Nafter hurting all those people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:36.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:45.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you did to innocent people \Nas you laughed about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.99,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:55.40,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Getting hurt and bleeding \Nare signs of being weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.86,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lack magic should just \Nget their asses beat by those
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:01.20,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,who are more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:08.04,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Especially... pieces of trash like \Nyou who don't have any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:12.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even those without magic \Ncan become the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to prove that by \Nbecoming the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:32.12,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Valtos! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.45,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I would've by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.07,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,That anti-magic is more \Ntroublesome than I'd imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:43.21,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're going to have \Nto take care of him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:56.47,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's gathering magic? What's heâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.89,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to attack using spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.43,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.70,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,How can I be panicking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.70,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I always need to remain calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:25.91,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Fuegoleon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:44.83,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... We can't \Nafford to lose Rades, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:50.23,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you all! Get away! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.11,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.63,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,We received orders from Master \Nto come here, and look at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:02.32,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,You're struggling against \Nthis lot. How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:28.68,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Such piercingly cold magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.79,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,There are five new enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:38.69,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I was only scratched... but thanks to \Nthat curse, the bleeding won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.49,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose any more blood, I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.29,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:49.25,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you should be thanking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.78,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,If we hadn't arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:55.96,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,you definitely would've been\Ncaptured and dissected alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.25,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're gonna be dissected, \NI want to be the one to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.17,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.58,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it looks like the tables have turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:19.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.03,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:25.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:35.25,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,This brat... He struck himself with his \Nown swords to get rid of the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.25,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable... He's so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:42.82,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's fun. Can I dissect him later?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:44.22,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.05,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Boo. You're such a spoilsport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:55.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All I've ever faced since \NI was born... was adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:21:00.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many come at me,\Nno matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:04.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blast them all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:09.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:33.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:38.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:43.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:49.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:51.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:54.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.62,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:00.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:03.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:05.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:08.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:10.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:13.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:19.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:25.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:28.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
