Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:43.75,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:47.84,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}They Won't Find Me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:46.39,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,They Won't Find Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:52.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold! He's not the spatial magic user.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:55.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That spell pinpointed him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:22:58.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no way the spellcaster \Ncould've cast it from far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:01.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Where could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:13.51,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,They won't find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:15.12,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:16.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:17.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:18.89,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:20.02,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:23.75,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my grand entrance \Nand surprise them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.06,0:23:27.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure they're not here.\NLet's go look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:28.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:32.25,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can find them first!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:32.25,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:36.84,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:43.58,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights, eat my cooking and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:47.02,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fight my battle in the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.75,main,chef,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 26: "Wounded Beasts."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:55.50,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 26\N\N{\fs18} Wounded Beasts
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:53.74,main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking food with magic is my job!
